    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"650294ec-a066-49f9-81d6-da15476d9305\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>You can find out all about Light Filters in the Renderman <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://renderman-26.refined.site/space/REN26/19661491/Light+Filters\" rel=\"nofollow\">documentation</a>.</p></div></div><h3 id=\"LightFilters-AddingLightFilter\">Adding Light Filter</h3><p>To add a light filter, in your OBJ pane, select the light filter in the TAB menu.  </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"408\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-58.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433137127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=236\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-58.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433137127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"356\" data-width=\"614\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645083\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2019-1-4_10-29-58.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645033\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"99bfdc77-916b-4217-8d45-51844eb2add2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-58.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433137127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=614&amp;height=356 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-58.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433137127&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=236 1x\"></span><p>Parent the light filter OBJ to the light OBJ if you want the filter to inherit the transformation from the light.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"408\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136952&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=202\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136952&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"298\" data-width=\"600\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645080\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2019-1-4_10-29-7.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645033\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"353babc3-f88f-4c7e-aff3-3fb7e6149b58\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136952&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=298 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/image2019-1-4_10-29-7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136952&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=202 1x\"></span><p>We can translate the light filter and scale it.  It is best to translate the light filter in Z away from the light to avoid seeing the edge of the light filter.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"278\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/lightfilterviewport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=278&amp;height=229\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645033/lightfilterviewport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"508\" data-width=\"616\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645071\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightfilterviewport.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645033\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fe6c3b36-3686-4fc1-9ae4-987a25e90f03\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/lightfilterviewport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=556&amp;height=458 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/lightfilterviewport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=278&amp;height=229 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"LightFilters-SetLightFilter\">Set Light Filter</h3><p>Drag your light filter VOP to the Light Filter shaders of your light.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg\" width=\"1109\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1109&amp;height=315\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645033/RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"315\" data-width=\"1109\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645047\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645033\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a68f7f9a-b54a-4274-96c6-9953e3e48dba\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1109&amp;height=315 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645033/RenderMan_RfH_LightFilter.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433136378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1109&amp;height=315 1x\"></span><p />"
